00:10:11.670 --> 00:10:12.840
Consigue a todos.

00:10:12.840 --> 00:10:14.120
Vayamos aquí.

00:10:14.120 --> 00:10:15.270
Dong. ¡Vamos!

00:10:16.910 --> 00:10:17.720
Buddy,

00:10:18.390 --> 00:10:19.630
